<http://www.spektrix.com/theporttheatre/event/38801AQDNRKLTDJNRGTHNNSDTQVMLRTCD> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "Cuban Vibes: Waves of Latin Jazz ";
  schema:description """
	 <span class=\"BoldText\">Experience the Essence: Waves of Latin Jazz at the Cuban Vibes Symphonic Festival</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Get ready for an unforgettable second night of the <span class=\"ItalicText\">Cuban Vibes: A Symphonic Festival</span>, where the vibrant spirit of Latin Jazz merges seamlessly with the heart and soul of Cuba. The evening promises a dazzling array of mesmerizing performances by world-renowned musicians who have captivated audiences across global arenas.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Immerse yourself in the lush melodies and irresistible syncopated rhythms that fill the night air with an electric energy. This is not just a concert; it’s a jubilant celebration of culture, rhythm, and the transcendent language of music that speaks to all. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Artists:<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Mayquel González</span>, trumpet    <span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Harold López-Nussa</span>, piano<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Ruy López-Nussa</span>, drums<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Yandy Martínez González</span>, double bass<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Roberto Vizcaino Jr.</span>, Cuban percussion<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Miguel de Armas,</span> piano<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Miguel Valdés</span>, trumpet, Cuban percussion<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Phil Dwyer</span>, saxophones
""";
