<http://www.spektrix.com/theporttheatre/event/14002AJLHTMKCRKHSQMKRQLMBKPQPVQDP> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "Dancing on Strings ";
  schema:description """
	CONDUCTOR: Cosette Justo Valdés<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Immerse yourself in a diverse musical journey with the Vancouver Island Symphony's upcoming concert, showcasing an exquisite blend of classical and contemporary works. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Under the masterful direction of Cosette Justo Valdés, experience the elegant charm of Grieg’s Holberg Suite, the vibrant rhythms of Bartok’s Romanian Folk Dances, and the playful energy of Britten’s Simple Symphony. Discover the rhythmic allure of Lopez-Gavilán’s Guaguancó. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Join us for an evening where tradition meets innovation in a celebration of string orchestra brilliance!<span><br/></span>
""";
