<http://www.spektrix.com/theporttheatre/event/45801APJPHDJMJCSGNSRNCNRNHDDTHVGL> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "FLEETWOOD MAGIC";
  schema:description """
	Fleetwood Magic Tribute Show masterfully transports audiences in sound and time through a musical journey performing Fleetwood Mac’s greatest hits, authentically recreating the sound, style and mystique of Fleetwood Mac’s most iconic line-up.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>With stunning vintage costumes, soaring vocals, period-accurate ins<span><br/></span>trumentation, and enchanting on-stage personas, Fleetwood Magic delivers a live experience that reminds fans why Fleetwood Mac remains legendary.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Relive timeless classics like “Rhiannon,” “Dreams,” “You Make Loving Fun,” “Say You Love Me,” “The Chain,” “Go Your Own Way.” Listeners have come to realize the ‘Rumours’ are true – Fleetwood Magic does indeed, deliver the magic! <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Captivating audiences across the Vancouver Lower Mainland and Western Canada, their shows have become a must see event for Fleetwood Mac music fans of all ages!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>For more information about Fleetwood Magic, please visit: <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.fleetwoodmagic.ca\">www.fleetwoodmagic.ca</a>
""";
