<http://www.spektrix.com/theporttheatre/event/55801ACGDGDJSRRGCLCBTPCSLTJTBNGSM> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "Island Fantasy Ball 2026";
  schema:description """
	An exciting and glamorous weekend of Ballroom and Latin dancing at its finest! <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This two-day event will feature some of the best athletes in the province vying for the BC Closed Standard & Latin Championship Titles.  These couples will also have the opportunity to match their skills alongside world class dancers in the International Standard and Latin Championship events.   <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>In addition, couples of all ages and all levels of ability will compete in the Waltz, Foxtrot, Tango, Cha Cha, Rumba, Jive, and more. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>A delicious gourmet buffet dinner will be served on both Saturday and Sunday evenings with a cash bar service.  You are invited to join us for this exciting weekend filled with the elegant and graceful Ballroom dances as well as the sexy, intricate and explosive energy of the Latin events. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The Sunday daytime session offers all levels of competitions including Juvenile, Junior, Youth, Adult and Senior couples.   <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Throughout the competitions we offer breaks for social dancing as well as top-notch entertainment by our highly skilled couples.  Sunday evening will culminate in a “Showcase\" of top dancers performing routines highlighting their skills, choreography, musicality and imagination.  Pure entertainment!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The full weekend schedule, additional details, seating plan and sponsorship opportunities are available at  <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.islandfantasyball.com\"> www.islandfantasyball.com</a>
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-05-16T19:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
