    schema:Event;
  schema:name "Majestic Mozart ";
  schema:description """
	CONDUCTOR: Cosette Justo Valdés<span><br/></span>GUEST ARTISTS: Paolo Bortolussi, flute; Hannah Addario-Berry, cello; Lani Krantz, harp; Christopher Lee, clarinet<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Join the Vancouver Island Symphony for an exhilarating evening as they unveil the world premiere of Dorothy Chang's newest work which showcases the virtuosic playing for our own principal musicians. The program intensifies with \"Sepulchre,\" crafted by celebrated Canadian composer Nicole Lizée, renowned for her breathtakingly inventive style. Concluding the dynamic lineup is Mozart's illustrious Symphony No. 41, ensuring a captivating musical experience throughout.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>
""";
