<http://www.spektrix.com/theporttheatre/event/50401ARMBCNTPHTPBVLQSVDRCMHSBBNBM> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "Morgan Wallen Tribute";
  schema:description """
	Morgan Wallen Tribute UK pays homage to every aspect of Wallen's iconic repertoire, delivering a performance that is as authentic as it is exhilarating. Featuring his Biggest hits, Whiskey Glasses, Last Night, You Proof, Wasted On You, Up Down plus many more.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Whether you're a die-hard fan or a newcomer to Wallen's music, this tribute promises an unforgettable evening filled with the energy and excitement of a live concert experience. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Don't missyour chance to witness the phenomenon of Wallen's music recreated on stage by the outstanding Morgan Wallen Tribute UK.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Get ready to sing along and celebrate the legacy of one of country music's brightest stars in this sensational tribute show.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/MorganWallenTributeUK \"> Facebook</a> <span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.morganwallentribute.uk/\"> Website</a>  
""";
