<http://www.spektrix.com/theporttheatre/event/47001AKGBPVRNLLTLGMHBTDTNRJQVNRCM> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "NANAIMO CONCERT BAND Spring Concert";
  schema:description """
	 NANAIMO CONCERT BAND will deliver what it has become best known and loved for since 1872… a program well played, always entertaining, and leaving the audience wanting more!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Under the Musical Direction of Dr. John Churchley Nanaimo Concert Band returns to the stage of the Port Theatre for their annual Spring concert performing music for Adventures in Space and at Sea.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Adventure is a combination of fear, anticipation, and excitement as explorers venture out into the great unknown. Nowhere has inspired great books, films, and music more than the uncharted ocean and the infinity of space. Our concert will provide a taste of this excitement with music from films like 2001: A Space Odyssey, Pirates of the Caribbean, and Interstellar, as well as music inspired by space and the sea including Holst’s Planets.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Spend a Sunday afternoon at the Port Theatre, Nanaimo’s premier waterfront theatre, attending a performance which all generations can enjoy together at an extremely affordable price.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Nanaimo Concert Band believes that there is nothing better than the live music experience shared with an audience. Music is powerful and live music is food for the senses.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Won't you join us?
""";
