<http://www.spektrix.com/theporttheatre/event/47601ALRPQQGLMRHLJRSGRRTJGJKMNSGT> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "SPICE WANNABE - The Spice Girls Tribute";
  schema:description """
	“SPICE WANNABE” is bringing us back to the 90’s with their high energy show, paying tribute to the best selling girl group of all time The Spice Girls! Live with five part harmonies, original choreography, iconic costumes and British accents, this Girl Power cast delivers a nostalgic experience that is sure to “Spice Up Your Life”!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Creating an electrifying atmosphere, this production has everyone singing and dancing along to the biggest Spice Girl hits including ‘Wannabe’, ‘2 Become 1’, ‘Say You’ll Be There’ , ‘Spice Up Your Life’, ‘Too Much’, and many more!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>“Spice Wannabe” is the USA’s Premiere Spice Girls Tribute show, live from the entertainment capital of the world, Las Vegas! After performing to a SOLD OUT crowd for their very first show in Las Vegas, the cast is taking the production on the road to wow audiences across the States and Worldwide. Equipped with professional tribute artists, musicians and back up dancers who are the best in the business, “Spice Wannabe” is an experience not to be missed!
""";
