<http://www.spektrix.com/theporttheatre/event/51801AMMMQBBLVKCCNBKCBSKVNJHHMGKP> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Big Heart Journey";
  schema:description """
	A heart-opening family experience of music, movement, and magic.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Created and performed by Taes Leavitt, two-time Juno Award-winning artist, musician, co-founder of the hit TV show <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://splashnboots.com/\"> Splash&#39;N Boots</a>, and founder of <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://bigheartjourney.com/\"> The Big Heart Journey</a>, this unforgettable live experience invites families to explore the beautiful world of feelings together.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Through music, dance, story, and interactive moments, audiences of all ages will laugh, move, and feel their way through joy, sadness, anger, love, and hope discovering that every feeling has a purpose and a place.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>It’s part concert, part movement, part magic, a heart-expanding celebration that will leave you feeling inspired, connected, and deeply alive.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All proceeds support Lumara, Grief & Bereavement Care - helping families find light, hope, and healing through loss.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://lumarasociety.org/\">Lumara Grief &amp; Bereavement Centre Society, Parksville</a>
""";
