<http://www.spektrix.com/theporttheatre/event/24401ANRSMNVVNPTCKDHLSQSTGQBDDKHJ> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "TOM GREEN";
  schema:description """
	Tom Green is a groundbreaking Canadian comedian, actor, and media pioneer known for his unpredictable MTV show, cult-classic films like Freddy Got Fingered, and for inspiring a generation through his early Internet talk show and podcasting. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>In addition to his return to Canada with a wave of new projects —including a documentary, comedy special, reality series, country album and his upcoming new Crave Original Series, Tom Green’s Funny Farm, which marks the first project in his new co-development deal with Bell Media — Tom is back on the road performing live stand-up comedy, bringing his signature style of humor to audiences worldwide.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Don’t miss an evening of Green’s hysterical comedy, along with stories about his career and a selection of original songs live. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/shorts/ilQSNJ9U18U\">Watch Tom Green GREAT TIME</a><span><br/></span>
""";
