  schema:name "WAR On The Catwalk";
  schema:description """
	Murray & Peter Present WAR On The Catwalk hosted by drag superstar Alyssa Edwards. Get ready for your favorite drag queens performing live on stage. We've got Jewels Sparkles, Lexi, Lydia B. Kollins, Bosco, Suzie Toot and Daya Betty. All ages welcome. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Get tour info at <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.DragFans.com\">www.DragFans.com</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">Meet & Greet available for purchase with the purchase of a ticket:</span><span><br/></span>This special add-on is an optional, separate purchase <span class=\"BoldText\">on top of each ticket purchase</span> and includes an exclusive photo opportunity with the entire cast on the main stage before the show. Purchasing fans also receive an official tour clack fan and a souvenir laminate with lanyard. Plus, get early access to purchase tour merch. (The queens will autograph any of their own merch purchased at the venue).
""";
